alerts.title: Green Warning For Ice Snow In Belgium - Coastal Zone
Orange Warning For Ice Snow In Belgium - Coastal Zone
alerts.description: Widespread slippery conditions on the ground are expected due to: 3 to 5 cm fresh snow in 1 hour, or 6 to 10 cm fresh snow in 6 hours, or 11 to 25 cm fresh snow in 24 hours, or widespread black ice or ice patches. Be careful and follow the instructions of the responsible authority.

alerts.title: Wind - Warnings For Vlissingen - The Netherlands
Yellow Warning For Ice Snow In Belgium - Coastal Zone
alerts.description: The ground may become slippery due to: 1 to 5 cm fresh snow in 6 hours, or 5 to 10 cm fresh snow in 24 hours, or (very) local black ice, or (very) local frost or ice patches. Be careful.
